description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured the women at the GD house Kyle stole from Kim in La Quinta, Kathy with a giant candle auditioning for Stomp, and Erika revealing more! On The Real Housewives of New York, the women are still in Salem and theres some broken glass and a psychic dinner.


RHONY Recap: 36:06ish
